1
00:00:13,400 --> 00:00:14,759
There's one way to cure Gut-Breaking Grass.

2
00:00:16,120 --> 00:00:16,920
What's the cure?

3
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:18,879
A life for a life.

4
00:00:19,879 --> 00:00:20,440
That's right.

5
00:00:21,559 --> 00:00:22,800
To save this friend of yours,

6
00:00:23,280 --> 00:00:24,440
it takes a life for a life.

7
00:00:25,079 --> 00:00:27,480
My brother stayed silent to help you.

8
00:00:28,760 --> 00:00:30,199
But since you're so insistent,

9
00:00:30,839 --> 00:00:33,359
he can help you trade your life for your friend's now.

10
00:00:35,960 --> 00:00:36,520
Great!

11
00:00:36,840 --> 00:00:37,719
Old Qian can be saved!

12
00:00:38,240 --> 00:00:38,640
Old Qian!

13
00:00:39,039 --> 00:00:39,880
You're going to be saved!

14
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:41,079
I'll save you, I'll save you.

15
00:00:41,079 --> 00:00:42,000
I'll trade my life for yours.

16
00:00:43,280 --> 00:00:45,000
Doctor, save me, doctor!

17
00:00:45,280 --> 00:00:45,920
Save me!

18
00:00:46,439 --> 00:00:47,479
You trade your life for his!

19
00:00:48,119 --> 00:00:49,960
Why should my brother's life pay for his?

20
00:00:51,200 --> 00:00:52,200
She's asking why.

21
00:00:53,079 --> 00:00:54,039
I'll tell you why.

22
00:00:56,759 --> 00:00:58,079
Because your brother is a doctor.

23
00:00:59,679 --> 00:01:01,320
Because of A healer's compassion.

24
00:01:02,679 --> 00:01:03,799
If he doesn't save him, who will?

25
00:01:04,519 --> 00:01:06,359
Doctors heal and save lives, right?

26
00:01:06,519 --> 00:01:07,359
Exactly!

27
00:01:07,560 --> 00:01:08,319
So saving lives is only natural.

28
00:01:08,319 --> 00:01:08,640
You...

29
00:01:10,400 --> 00:01:11,040
Ren Feifan.

30
00:01:12,159 --> 00:01:13,760
You may refuse to save Old Qian today,

31
00:01:15,840 --> 00:01:18,319
but Premier Medical Hall's signboard,

32
00:01:18,319 --> 00:01:19,239
I will definitely

33
00:01:19,599 --> 00:01:20,359
tear it down.

34
00:01:21,359 --> 00:01:22,079
How dare you!

35
00:01:25,239 --> 00:01:26,040
Young Master Wang.

36
00:01:28,359 --> 00:01:29,480
Do you still remember me?

37
00:01:32,359 --> 00:01:34,480
I'm also a doctor of Premier Medical Hall.

38
00:01:35,760 --> 00:01:37,680
Him — I'll save him.

39
00:01:38,920 --> 00:01:41,760
Don't you dare touch our signboard.

40
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:48,959
Young Master, seal his meridians first.

41
00:01:49,760 --> 00:01:54,120
Otherwise, I couldn't save him even if I died twice.

42
00:01:54,640 --> 00:01:55,359
Young Master.

43
00:01:55,879 --> 00:01:56,400
Follow me.

44
00:02:23,680 --> 00:02:24,479
Young Master.

45
00:02:26,280 --> 00:02:27,280
Check my pulse.

46
00:02:38,919 --> 00:02:39,560
This is...

47
00:02:40,159 --> 00:02:41,039
a Fatal Pulse.

48
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:47,039
Young Master.

49
00:02:48,360 --> 00:02:50,439
I don't have much time left.

50
00:02:51,840 --> 00:02:55,800
If I can save Premier Medical Hall's name before I go,

51
00:02:56,759 --> 00:02:58,319
I'll die without regrets.

52
00:02:59,199 --> 00:02:59,840
Master Zhang.

53
00:03:00,719 --> 00:03:01,879
The toxins in your body

54
00:03:02,159 --> 00:03:04,039
came from years of preparing herbs.

55
00:03:04,560 --> 00:03:05,479
I can find a way.

56
00:03:05,759 --> 00:03:06,960
Though I can't cure it completely,

57
00:03:07,280 --> 00:03:09,280
I can prolong your life as much as possible.

58
00:03:10,639 --> 00:03:11,240
Besides,

59
00:03:11,439 --> 00:03:13,879
Today's incident is a trap set by Wang Wenhao.

60
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:16,120
I can shut Premier Medical Hall down.

61
00:03:16,240 --> 00:03:17,879
I can even take the signboard down.

62
00:03:18,639 --> 00:03:19,400
But your life,

63
00:03:20,560 --> 00:03:22,039
I will definitely save it.

64
00:03:22,719 --> 00:03:24,120
My days are numbered.

65
00:03:24,479 --> 00:03:25,719
Living is suffering.

66
00:03:26,520 --> 00:03:27,280
Dying

67
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:28,879
would be a release.

68
00:03:32,319 --> 00:03:35,240
Your father recognized my worth.

69
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:40,439
I've worked half my life with a true friend,

70
00:03:41,319 --> 00:03:43,960
I'm already content.

71
00:03:45,960 --> 00:03:48,639
If you save my life today,

72
00:03:51,479 --> 00:03:54,360
we'll lose not just Premier Medical Hall's signboard,

73
00:03:55,400 --> 00:03:58,240
but also our ancestors' teachings.

74
00:04:01,639 --> 00:04:02,319
You

75
00:04:03,439 --> 00:04:04,319
can afford that loss,

76
00:04:05,039 --> 00:04:06,800
but I cannot!

77
00:04:08,039 --> 00:04:11,000
True, this is Wang Wenhao's trap.

78
00:04:11,520 --> 00:04:14,599
But if you don't save him today,

79
00:04:14,680 --> 00:04:17,720
you'll be shutting out everyone outside

80
00:04:17,759 --> 00:04:19,000
who believes in us.

81
00:04:20,040 --> 00:04:21,720
Can you do that?

82
00:04:24,839 --> 00:04:25,279
I...

83
00:04:25,279 --> 00:04:28,240
Young Master, become a great healer!

84
00:04:28,439 --> 00:04:29,759
To shelter all humanity,

85
00:04:29,800 --> 00:04:32,399
to save the common folk!

86
00:04:35,759 --> 00:04:36,959
Go prepare.

87
00:04:37,160 --> 00:04:39,519
Even if you don't save him today,

88
00:04:40,040 --> 00:04:42,040
I'll die beneath this plaque anyway.

89
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:43,600
Die to prove my resolve.

90
00:04:49,279 --> 00:04:50,439
Feifan is humbled by your lesson.

91
00:04:52,560 --> 00:04:53,600
At this moment,

92
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:56,199
what I can't let go of most

93
00:04:57,079 --> 00:04:58,839
is my little granddaughter.

94
00:05:00,519 --> 00:05:01,360
After I'm gone,

95
00:05:02,079 --> 00:05:02,959
Young Master,

96
00:05:03,879 --> 00:05:08,399
will you shelter her, protect her, and teach her?

97
00:05:12,439 --> 00:05:13,040
Everyone.

98
00:05:16,399 --> 00:05:19,240
This is Zhang Cheng, our doctor at Premier Medical Hall.

99
00:05:20,480 --> 00:05:23,040
Doctor Zhang is willing to sacrifice himself today to save this patient.

100
00:05:23,600 --> 00:05:25,199
So with all of you as witnesses,

101
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:27,720
watch how I save this patient.

102
00:05:28,680 --> 00:05:29,959
I hope after this,

103
00:05:31,639 --> 00:05:33,759
you'll all trust Premier Medical Hall from now on.

104
00:05:35,279 --> 00:05:36,120
This, this...

105
00:05:36,120 --> 00:05:37,240
A healer's compassion!

106
00:05:37,279 --> 00:05:38,920
Truly A healer's compassion!

107
00:05:38,920 --> 00:05:39,839
A man of great righteousness!

108
00:05:39,839 --> 00:05:40,480
A life for a life!

109
00:05:40,480 --> 00:05:41,199
Indeed.

110
00:06:17,399 --> 00:06:19,120
Thank you, Mr. Wang, for this generous gift.

111
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:22,560
Feifan will repay you handsomely one day.

112
00:06:30,399 --> 00:06:31,360
He's truly a miracle healer!

113
00:06:31,360 --> 00:06:32,120
He actually saved him!

114
00:06:32,120 --> 00:06:33,959
He truly traded his own life to save another.

115
00:06:35,959 --> 00:06:37,040
Thank you for saving my friend.

116
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:04,560
Yueyue.

117
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:06,680
Grandpa, you're awake.

118
00:07:09,480 --> 00:07:10,720
Where am I?

119
00:07:11,600 --> 00:07:13,560
I'm not dead?

120
00:07:14,879 --> 00:07:15,519
Master Zhang.

121
00:07:16,360 --> 00:07:17,319
You're safe now.

122
00:07:18,399 --> 00:07:19,399
I brought you home.

123
00:07:19,720 --> 00:07:22,639
Gut-Breaking Grass, aside from a life for a life,

124
00:07:24,079 --> 00:07:25,240
has no antidote.

125
00:07:26,759 --> 00:07:28,000
Here's the thing, Master Zhang.

126
00:07:28,759 --> 00:07:29,959
The poisoned patient

127
00:07:30,480 --> 00:07:31,600
had very little toxin in his body,

128
00:07:32,319 --> 00:07:33,199
and the poisoning was mild.

129
00:07:33,959 --> 00:07:34,920
I'm guessing

130
00:07:34,959 --> 00:07:37,680
he took the Gut-Breaking Grass just before entering Premier Medical Hall.

131
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:40,839
Then he spat some out when Wang Wenhao wasn't looking.

132
00:07:41,480 --> 00:07:45,639
His chest and cuffs both reeked of Gut-Breaking Grass.

133
00:07:48,079 --> 00:07:49,279
Everyone fears death.

134
00:07:50,519 --> 00:07:51,079
Of course,

135
00:07:52,079 --> 00:07:52,920
there are exceptions.

136
00:07:54,720 --> 00:07:55,600
Except for you.

137
00:07:58,079 --> 00:07:59,319
A man of great righteousness.

138
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:01,600
A man of great righteousness.

139
00:08:03,439 --> 00:08:07,680
You little brat, you dare joke with me now.

140
00:08:12,199 --> 00:08:13,720
Though no life needed to be traded,

141
00:08:14,240 --> 00:08:17,160
then why did I pass out earlier?

142
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:21,519
Wang Wenhao used despicable tactics.

143
00:08:22,160 --> 00:08:23,519
To force his man to take the poison,

144
00:08:24,120 --> 00:08:25,639
he must have threatened his family.

145
00:08:26,600 --> 00:08:28,600
If Wang realized he spat out the poison,

146
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:30,920
it would endanger his entire family.

147
00:08:31,680 --> 00:08:34,879
So I just let Wang Wenhao think he'd gained the upper hand.

148
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:36,399
That makes sense.

149
00:08:38,759 --> 00:08:41,559
Then you and Yue'er should rest at home for now.

150
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:42,840
Don't go outside.

151
00:08:44,120 --> 00:08:45,600
Wait until I've dealt with the Wang family completely.

152
00:08:50,519 --> 00:08:53,000
That day will come soon.

153
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:00,919
I'll draw the poison out for you.

154
00:09:33,519 --> 00:09:34,159
Ruo Jin.

155
00:09:37,639 --> 00:09:39,000
You went to see that Ren Feifan again.

156
00:09:39,559 --> 00:09:41,000
Last time you came back covered in injuries,

157
00:09:41,039 --> 00:09:42,120
and they still haven't healed.

158
00:09:42,440 --> 00:09:43,799
You're the one who put him behind bars.

159
00:09:44,240 --> 00:09:45,879
And you're the one who insisted on keeping the baby.

160
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:46,960
Think about it.

161
00:09:47,279 --> 00:09:48,960
Will he forgive you because of this child?

162
00:09:51,240 --> 00:09:52,600
Whether he forgives me or not,

163
00:09:53,240 --> 00:09:54,679
it won't change the fact that I love him.

164
00:09:54,679 --> 00:09:55,039
You...

165
00:10:00,039 --> 00:10:00,600
Mom.

166
00:10:00,600 --> 00:10:01,200
Don't call me that.

167
00:10:01,759 --> 00:10:03,879
I just can't see what's so great about Ren Feifan.

168
00:10:04,559 --> 00:10:06,519
His background and family are nothing compared to yours.

169
00:10:06,879 --> 00:10:09,399
He's only with you to marry up into our family.

170
00:10:09,759 --> 00:10:11,639
You're already engaged to Wang Wenhao.

171
00:10:12,240 --> 00:10:14,080
Wang Wenhao is the sole heir of the Wang family.

172
00:10:14,639 --> 00:10:16,960
He'll inherit the entire Wang Group one day.

173
00:10:17,679 --> 00:10:20,399
Daughter, use your head and think it through.

174
00:10:25,320 --> 00:10:25,960
Wenhao.

175
00:10:26,480 --> 00:10:27,279
Yes, yes.

176
00:10:29,360 --> 00:10:30,039
No problem.

177
00:10:32,240 --> 00:10:33,840
Wenhao's invited you over for dinner.

178
00:10:34,159 --> 00:10:35,279
Get yourself ready.

179
00:10:35,279 --> 00:10:36,159
Dress up nicely.

180
00:10:38,600 --> 00:10:40,120
Don't upset his family again.

181
00:10:40,679 --> 00:10:42,039
Think about that child of yours.
